''kono sora wo daite kagayaku shoonen yo shinwa ni nare''

16
00:01:56,450 --> 00:01:58,650
Hey, where's Asuka ?

17
00:01:58,650 --> 00:02:03,650
She's already gone.
She's trying to avoid me.

18
00:02:03,650 --> 00:02:05,150
Why ?

19
00:02:05,150 --> 00:02:08,250
Shin-chan, it seems women's hearts are still too hard for you to understand.

20
00:02:11,450 --> 00:02:12,450
Umm...

21
00:02:11,450 --> 00:02:12,450
By the way...

22
00:02:13,450 --> 00:02:14,650
Go ahead.

23
00:02:14,650 --> 00:02:18,250
Is the rumor about
Unit 04 being lost true ?

24
00:02:18,250 --> 00:02:20,950
I heard it was
destroyed in an accident.

25
00:02:20,950 --> 00:02:26,850
Yes, it's true. Unit 04's gone,
along with NERV 2nd Branch.

26
00:02:26,850 --> 00:02:29,350
It was during the
``S2'' engine test.

27
00:02:30,050 --> 00:02:33,550
We're alright here, though.
All three units are working fine.

28
00:02:33,550 --> 00:02:35,950
The pilots and staff
are both excellent, too.

29
00:02:35,950 --> 00:02:38,950
But I heard Unit 03
is coming from the U.S...

30
00:02:38,950 --> 00:02:41,150
The activation test will take
place at Matsushiro, right ?

31
00:02:41,150 --> 00:02:46,950
Yeah. I'll be gone about 4 days. But don't worry, Kaji will take care of you guys.

32
00:02:46,950 --> 00:02:48,250
But what about the test ?

33
00:02:48,250 --> 00:02:51,350
Since Ritsuko will be there,
there won't be any problems.

34
00:02:51,350 --> 00:02:53,050
But what about the pilot ?

35
00:02:54,050 --> 00:02:56,150
Well, about the pilot...

36
00:03:03,550 --> 00:03:04,050
Coming !

37
00:03:05,050 --> 00:03:07,150
Good morning, ma'am !

38
00:03:07,150 --> 00:03:10,650
I came here today to make
a request of Major Katsuragi.

39
00:03:10,650 --> 00:03:14,950
Please, make me the pilot
of Evangelion Unit 03.

